<subSubSection pageId="4" pageNumber="5" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="4.[264,1323,283,790]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[312,452,724,750]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Etymology.</emphasis>
Named in honour of Mateus Pepinelli, our friend, who has contributed much to our studies of the 
<taxonomicName box="[576,744,764,790]" class="Insecta" family="Chironomidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Chironomidae</taxonomicName>
and who collected the 
<typeStatus box="[1015,1121,764,790]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">holotype</typeStatus>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
